      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SETTLE FOR LESS (7) sizzled around this track over 350m in 18.76 for a 5 length success. In form and rates on top again. EXTRA VOLTAGE (1) was in the minors two back then strongly fancied last time at Capalaba where he led until late, recording another placing when second (20.18) in a Grade 5. Has a good record at this journey. Expected to be in the finish again. GRUBBER KICK (5) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 19.30. Jumping from the pinch draw but goes well over this trip. Form should stack up. KILL YOUR SMILE (2) can find the frame without surprising.",
